5. Voiceflow Responsibilities

Voiceflow is responsible for:

Starting conversations
Collecting user messages
Calling Flask APIs
Showing AI responses
Managing conversation flow
Displaying chatbot UI

Voiceflow does not replace Flask or Gemini.

6. What Does Flask Do?

Flask handles:

Business logic
API endpoints
Gemini communication
Order processing
Google Sheets integration

7. Voiceflow vs Flask
   ------------------

| Voiceflow           | Flask              |
| ------------------- | ------------------ |
| Conversation Design | Backend Logic      |
| Chat Interface      | Python Programming |
| API Calls           | API Creation       |
| Variables           | Business Logic     |
| User Flow           | AI Integration     |

======

8. Voiceflow Blocks

Voiceflow projects are built using blocks.

Example

Start
   │
   ▼
Speak
   │
   ▼
Capture
   │
   ▼
API
   │
   ▼
Condition
   │
   ▼
End

Each block has a specific purpose.

9. Important Voiceflow Blocks

| Block     | Purpose             |
| --------- | ------------------- |
| Start     | Starts chatbot      |
| Speak     | Sends message       |
| Capture   | Receives user input |
| API       | Calls Flask API     |
| Condition | Decision making     |
| End       | Ends conversation   |


