11. API Communication

Voiceflow communicates with Flask using HTTP.

Example

POST

/chat

Voiceflow sends

{
   "message":"Suggest pizza"
}

Flask returns

{
   "response":"I recommend Veg Pizza."
}

Voiceflow displays

I recommend Veg Pizza.

===========

12. Thread (Conversation)

Each customer has their own conversation.

Customer A

↓

Conversation A

---------------------

Customer B

↓

Conversation B

Each conversation remains separate.

This allows the chatbot to remember context during a session.

